thread.title: Two package blasts this month believed to be linked: Austin police

title: Two package blasts this month believed to be linked: Austin police
text:
Two package blasts this month believed to be linked: Austin police 6:04pm GMT - 01:49 
Austin Police Chief Brian Manley said the package explosion in Austin, Texas, Monday morning that killed a 17-year-old boy had similarities to another package explosion earlier this month that killed a man. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
